Package blf.grammar

Interface BcqlListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseBlockchainListener, BaseGenerator, BcqlBaseListener, EmitAnalyzer, EthereumListener, ExpressionStatementAnalyzer, FilterDefinitionAnalyzer, FilterNestingAnalyzer, HyperledgerListener, ItemGenerator, RootListener, SemanticAnalysis, SemanticAnalyzer, VariableExistenceListener
    public interface BcqlListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by BcqlParser.
